messages.message:
If anyone else wants to take a look at this strange bug, that would be great, here is what happens:
Run this flow (in binary mode): https://instabase.com/apps/flow/edit/ib_solutions/solutions/fs/Instabase%20Drive/training/Adverse%20News%20Training%20Example/workflow.ibflow#
If you run the entire Flow as a whole, the result of merge files is an empty list even though there are clearly inputs. If you run step by step (in binary mode), the result of merge files is only ~10 or so of the files from the previous step.
